PREREQUISITE:
create a tmpfs mounted volume for your MXL domain.

mount -t tmpfs -o size=512m tmpfs /Volumes/mxl

mxl-gst-looping-filesrc

**To run this app you need to use the shell script run-loop-player.sh because of a Gstreamer library dependency.

mxl-gst-looping-filesrc 

./mxl-gst-looping-filesrc [OPTIONS]


OPTIONS:
  -h,     --help              Print this help message and exit 
  -d,     --domain TEXT REQUIRED 
                              The MXL domain directory 
  -i,     --input TEXT:FILE REQUIRED 
                              MPEGTS media file location 

This app only do video for now, here is an example to run it with the sizzle.ts file provided.

./run-loop-player.sh -d /Volumes/mxl -i sizzle.ts